                           <q xml:lang="en">
                            This (is) the gospel of Beta Masqal, that I Bǝqʷāʿ la-Ṣǝyon donated. Might God absolve my sins and delete my mistakes. You, who read, pray for me, 
                            bless me and do not bring this (book) away to another region.
                           </q>
